RAR in CLASH clusters is consistent with predictions from a\nsemi-analytical model developed in the standard $\\Lambda$CDM framework. Our\nresults also predict the presence of a baryonic Faber--Jackson relation\n($\\sigma_v^4\\propto M_\\mathrm{bar}$) on cluster scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 02:07:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Apr 2020 13:46:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-17"}
