and their ratio can be used to discriminate different\nflavor transition scenarios of SN neutrinos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 14:22:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Mar 2020 14:03:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 16:05:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 31 Dec 2021 03:14:16 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 11 Mar 2023 14:16:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
