clusions}$ The proposed framework provides an efficient\nalternative to microscopic approaches based on the evolution of the system in a\nspace of collective coordinates all the way to scission. It can be used to\ncarry out global calculations of fission fragment distributions across the\nr-process region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 15:54:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2020 18:58:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
