ulations show that FDRN\nobtains the enhanced recognition results, compared with other related models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 06:55:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Apr 2020 08:44:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 10:47:35 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2021 02:35:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-10"}
